CL AL WEHRLEY

  

SPECIFICATION CHANGE
S336, Addendum

Specification change 83-36 includes several SIR WALTER RALEIGH

Packaging changes.

‘The SIR WALTER RALEIGH Aromatic pouch foil changed from material

35-008 to 35-012 on August 10, 1983. This change 1s to the shorter

flap, and is for both domestic end export.

Please file the attached and return the old.

forbs

73, P. Markhan/ja/21130
